{"tid":332650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"時代的眼淚‼️小栗有以也有被公開處刊的一天‼️","createTime":"2017-07-23T07:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T09:06:47.000Z","uid":16063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2eb89c724bff10d485f8ced85f051ffe64ca80","tid":332650,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"曾經，小栗有以是可愛的代名詞，可愛值之高無人能敵，「原來真的有兩年年一遇的女生！」是當時宅宅們第一次看到ゆいゆい時的驚嘆。然而，隨著時間過去，今日一張ゆいゆい被「公開處刑」的照片，讓不少粉絲看過後感嘆，「真是長江前浪推後浪，時代的眼淚啊QQ。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駒駒這邊先解釋一下什麼是公開處刑好了，所謂的處刑技，就是當一個顏值破表的藝人和其他普通藝人一起出席活動或拍照時，兩相比較，對方1秒被比下去，對比超明顯，對靠臉吃飯的藝人來說，就是處刑無誤。該技能可單放也可打範圍，人多時效果更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面這張照片就是近日指原莉乃和小栗有以的合照，從前網友們都會大讚ゆいゆい（小栗有以綽號）好正、雙馬尾就是神之類的，可是那已經曾經，現在的網友對於這張照片的評論是：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFZeX1GXUAIRP17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFZeX1GXUAIRP17.jpg&h=6d451ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFZeX1HW0AIOkc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFZeX1HW0AIOkc6.jpg&h=da26c654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「指原醬真的好美！」<br />\n「傻西！傻西！」（指原的日文諧音）<br />\n「小栗有以居然也有被公開處刑一天...」<br />\n「我還是比較喜歡橋本陽菜」<br />\n「指原莉乃的成長真的沒有極限啊！」<br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，和以往相比，視線已經不會只在ゆいゆい身上，這就是時代的眼淚啊QQ。"},{"pid":"333fcbd0cfc4bbd6c04c91eb7b3523555915839f","tid":332650,"uid":58,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/135849_8760b22dbb611cace0eff86617ee67f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F135849_8760b22dbb611cace0eff86617ee67f1.jpg&h=62469142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2367a2bb09b003bc277de77e1ffbd23bffc87428","tid":332650,"uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b685202aa31edc55837bcca67695d35124b2764","tid":332650,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"禾指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344f8a8018777dd4a01b19bd3ac11251be8de1cd","tid":332650,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"禾指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17619bf80b8fa67ae0b6f8891379ad5d4946075a","tid":332650,"uid":3652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"低汁"},{"pid":"9aa428f986d24f3de75afa1719ead81c1585f79d","tid":332650,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>低汁</blockquote><br />\n你100句有99句都係罵我或者ゆいゆい架啦🤷&zwj;♀️‼️"},{"pid":"fba33590b0adfacc92154dda0baf72620a597b13","tid":332650,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"禾指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e172c11b42461b123a746ecd25c64255156496","tid":332650,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"「原來真的有兩年年一遇的女生！」<br />\n<br />\n樓主呢句打多咗一個年字‼️"},{"pid":"c831284f76d2643528e987ce728fb6a29f44195e","tid":332650,"uid":34333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"幾時改生駒版"},{"pid":"b802080ce600bf9916715734cee1def2585272c4","tid":332650,"uid":33563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"「我還是比較喜歡橋本陽菜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381d9e791b58dea90196e33f4af8352d04626ee3","tid":332650,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff2576d2a349a59e1ec